                        </div>
                        <div class="benefits__card-title">
                            Welcome to Odigo!
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefits__card-subtitle">
                            Jump off balcony, onto stranger's head. Chase ball of string hide when guests come over.
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefits__card-button">
                            <a href="#" class="benefits__card-link">LEARN MORE</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefits__card">
                        <div class="benefits__card-pic">
                            <img src="/img/main/benefits/icon_2.svg" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefits__card-title">
                            Your Personal Japan Guide
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefits__card-subtitle">
                            Jump off balcony, onto stranger's head. Chase ball of string hide when guests come over.
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefits__card-button">
                            <a href="#" class="benefits__card-link">LEARN MORE</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefits__card">
                        <div class="benefits__card-pic">
                            <img src="/img/main/benefits/icon_3.svg" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefits__card-title">
